\subsection*{R Code}

All analysis was conducted in R \Sexpr{R.version$major}.\Sexpr{R.version$minor}
\citep{rcore2024}. LDA, QDA, and NMDS used the \texttt{MASS} package
\citep{venables2002}. Note: the data file carries a \texttt{.csv} extension but is
structured as an Excel workbook (\texttt{xlsx}); \texttt{readxl::read\_excel()} detects
the format from the file header and reads it correctly.
